    <item>
      <title>API Config</title>
      <link>https://vuepress-theme-hope.github.io/copy-code/config/</link>
      <guid>https://vuepress-theme-hope.github.io/copy-code/config/</guid>
      <source url="https://vuepress-theme-hope.github.io/copy-code/rss.xml">API Config</source>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 id="baselang"> baseLang</h2>
<ul>
<li>Type: <code>string</code></li>
<li>Default: <code>'en-US'</code></li>
</ul>
<p>The language of the home directory.</p>
<h3 id="selector"> selector</h3>
<ul>
<li>Type: <code>string | string[]</code></li>
<li>Default: <code>'.theme-default-content div[class*=&quot;language-&quot;] pre'</code></li>
</ul>
<p>Code block selector</p>
<h3 id="duration"> duration</h3>
<ul>
<li>Type: <code>number</code></li>
<li>Default: <code>300</code></li>
</ul>
<p>Prompt message display time</p>
<h3 id="showinmobile"> showInMobile</h3>
<ul>
<li>Type: <code>boolean</code></li>
<li>Default: <code>false</code></li>
</ul>
<p>Whether to display on the mobile side</p>
]]></content:encoded>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Guide</title>
      <link>https://vuepress-theme-hope.github.io/copy-code/guide/</link>
      <guid>https://vuepress-theme-hope.github.io/copy-code/guide/</guid>
      <source url="https://vuepress-theme-hope.github.io/copy-code/rss.xml">Guide</source>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 id="usage"> Usage</h2>
<p>After enabling, this plugin will automatically add a copy button to the bottom right corner of each code block.</p>
<div><p>Tips</p>
<p>By default, the button is only displayed on desktop mode.</p>
</div>
<h2 id="effect"> Effect</h2>
<div><pre><code><span>// .vuepress/config.js</span>
module<span>.</span>exports <span>=</span> <span>{</span>
  plugins<span>:</span> <span>[</span>
    <span>[</span>
      <span>"@mr-hope/copy-code"</span><span>,</span>
      <span>{</span>
        <span>// your options</span>
      <span>}</span><span>,</span>
    <span>]</span><span>,</span>
  <span>]</span><span>,</span>
<span>}</span><span>;</span>
</code></pre>
<div><span>1</span><br><span>2</span><br><span>3</span><br><span>4</span><br><span>5</span><br><span>6</span><br><span>7</span><br><span>8</span><br><span>9</span><br><span>10</span><br><span>11</span><br></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
    </item>
    <item>
