<CodeGroup>
<CodeGroupItem title="yarn">
<div><pre><code><span>yarn</span> <span>add</span> -D @mr-hope/vuepress-plugin-copy-code
</code></pre>
<div><span>1</span><br></div></div></CodeGroupItem>
<CodeGroupItem title="npm">
<div><pre><code><span>npm</span> i -D @mr-hope/vuepress-plugin-copy-code
</code></pre>
<div><span>1</span><br></div></div></CodeGroupItem>
</CodeGroup>
<h3 id="usage"> Usage</h3>
<div><pre><code><span>// .vuepress/config.js</span>
module<span>.</span>exports <span>=</span> <span>{</span>
  plugins<span>:</span> <span>[</span>
    <span>[</span>
      <span>"@mr-hope/copy-code"</span><span>,</span>
      <span>{</span>
        <span>// your options</span>
      <span>}</span><span>,</span>
    <span>]</span><span>,</span>
  <span>]</span><span>,</span>
<span>}</span><span>;</span>
</code></pre>
<div><span>1</span><br><span>2</span><br><span>3</span><br><span>4</span><br><span>5</span><br><span>6</span><br><span>7</span><br><span>8</span><br><span>9</span><br><span>10</span><br><span>11</span><br></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>配置</title>
      <link>https://vuepress-theme-hope.github.io/copy-code/zh/config/</link>
      <guid>https://vuepress-theme-hope.github.io/copy-code/zh/config/</guid>
      <source url="https://vuepress-theme-hope.github.io/copy-code/rss.xml">配置</source>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 id="插件配置"> 插件配置</h2>
<h3 id="baselang"> baseLang</h3>
<ul>
<li>类型: <code>string</code></li>
<li>默认值: <code>'en-US'</code></li>
</ul>
<p>主目录所对应的语言。</p>
<h3 id="selector"> selector</h3>
<ul>
<li>类型: <code>string | string[]</code></li>
<li>默认值: <code>'.theme-default-content div[class*=&quot;language-&quot;] pre'</code></li>
</ul>
<p>代码块选择器</p>
<h3 id="duration"> duration</h3>
<ul>
<li>类型: <code>number</code></li>
<li>默认值: <code>300</code></li>
</ul>
<p>提示消息显示时间</p>
<h3 id="showinmobile"> showInMobile</h3>
<ul>
<li>类型: <code>boolean</code></li>
<li>默认值: <code>false</code></li>
</ul>
<p>是否展示在移动端</p>
]]></content:encoded>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>指南</title>
      <link>https://vuepress-theme-hope.github.io/copy-code/zh/guide/</link>
      <guid>https://vuepress-theme-hope.github.io/copy-code/zh/guide/</guid>
      <source url="https://vuepress-theme-hope.github.io/copy-code/rss.xml">指南</source>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 id="使用"> 使用</h2>
<p>启用后，本插件会自动添加复制按钮到每个代码块的右下角。</p>
<div><p>Tips</p>
<p>默认情况下，按钮仅在桌面模式显示。</p>
</div>
<h2 id="效果"> 效果</h2>
<div><pre><code><span>// .vuepress/config.js</span>
module<span>.</span>exports <span>=</span> <span>{</span>
  plugins<span>:</span> <span>[</span>
    <span>[</span>
      <span>"@mr-hope/copy-code"</span><span>,</span>
      <span>{</span>
        <span>// 你的选项</span>
      <span>}</span><span>,</span>
    <span>]</span><span>,</span>
  <span>]</span><span>,</span>
<span>}</span><span>;</span>
</code></pre>
<div><span>1</span><br><span>2</span><br><span>3</span><br><span>4</span><br><span>5</span><br><span>6</span><br><span>7</span><br><span>8</span><br><span>9</span><br><span>10</span><br><span>11</span><br></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
    </item>
